CITY RAT: Streetwise urban survivor

The City Rat is the quintessential urban survivor, equally at home in
Coalition megacities and free-town black markets. Streetwise,
quick-fingered, and connected, they navigate the shadows of
civilization with ease.

City Rats begin with a solid package of criminal and social skills and
have a generous number of picks from Rogue, Technical, and Physical
categories.

STARTING PACKAGE
  Attribute requirements: None. Any OCC-eligible race may choose City
    Rat.
  Equipment: Street clothes, lock pick set, laser pistol or revolver,
    and a network of contacts and credits.

